The paper focuses on the use of social media data for crisis response and management, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) and social media (cs.SI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with multimodal data, specifically textual and imagery content, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques for analyzing textual content and crisis management (cs.CR) tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR, cs.SI, and cs.MM, followed by cs.CL and cs.CR.
